> I'm about to go hunting through the local boneyards for middle and rear
> seats for my '79 bus, and may even scout for front seats as well.  Can
anyone
> tell me what years of bus/vanagon seats will fit?


Not sure about middle or rear.  But '77-91 fronts interchange. However you
may have to remove either the outside armrest or the fresh air conduit on
the door if using a Vanagon seat with armrests.

